"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"anonymous\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5147:\"<div>\n<h3>WordPress a eu 10 ans</h3>\n<p>Gros &eacute;cho en ligne :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>M&ecirc;me <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.lemonde.fr/technologies/article/2013/05/29/wordpress-a-dix-ans_3419808_651865.html\">Le Monde</a> a r&eacute;alis&eacute; un article.</li>\n<li>Le Journal du Net explique <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.journaldunet.com/solutions/saas-logiciel/10-ans-de-wordpress-0513.shtml\">les raisons du succ&egrave;s</a>.</li>\n<li>Clubic y va aussi de <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://pro.clubic.com/creation-de-site-web/cms-blog/actualite-561562-wordpress-cms-blog-open-source-php.html\">son petit article</a>.</li>\n<li>PC World termine sur <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.pcworld.fr/internet/actualites,wordpress-souffle-10-premieres-bougies,538931,1.htm\">une note ironique</a>&nbsp;:)</li>\n<li>WPMU donne un <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wpmu.org/wordpress-10-years-old-visual-history/\">historique des interfaces</a>.</li>\n<li>&hellip;ce qu&rsquo;avait fait <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.insidedaweb.com/wordpress-seo/historique-wordpress-10-ans-b2-cafelog-wordpress-3-2/\">InsideDaWeb en f&eacute;vrier</a> !</li>\n<li>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wpchannel.com/10-ans-wordpress/\">WordPress Channel </a>en a parl&eacute;.</li>\n<li>Presse-Citron salue l&rsquo;&eacute;v&egrave;nement&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.presse-citron.net/wordpress-10eme-anniversaire-infographie\">avec une infographie</a>.</li>\n<li>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vingthuitzerotrois.fr/wordpress/wordpress-fete-ses-ans-15246/\">2803</a>&nbsp;aborde le sujet.</li>\n<li>L&rsquo;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.florence-cann.com/2013/05/joyeux-anniversaire-wordpress/\">article de Florence Cann</a>.</li>\n<li>Sur le <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://gabale.fr/?p=2929\">blog de Gabale</a>.</li>\n<li>&hellip;et de nombreux autres blogs !</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Pas d&rsquo;interface de format de contenu dans WordPress 3.6</h3>\n<p>La d&eacute;cision a &eacute;t&eacute; prise contrainte et forc&eacute;e. L&rsquo;interface pr&eacute;vue des <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/05/29/post-formats-ui-is-exiting-core-will-live-as-a-plugin/\">formats de contenu ne sera pas int&eacute;gr&eacute;e dans WordPress 3.6</a>. Une extension pourra permettre de retrouver la fonction.</p>\n<h3>Jetpack am&eacute;liore son mode galerie</h3>\n<p>Le mode galerie photo de <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://jetpack.me/2013/05/25/tiled-galleries/\">Jetpack propose de faire des galerie originales</a>&nbsp;(en) avec des formes diff&eacute;rentes.</p>\n<h3>WordPress pour Android 2.4 en beta</h3>\n<p>Si vous souhaitez tester la version <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://make.wordpress.org/mobile/2013/05/24/wp-android-beta/\">2.4 beta de WordPress pour Android, c&rsquo;est ici</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>CMS : les meilleures solutions</h3>\n<p>Le <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.journaldunet.com/solutions/saas-logiciel/cms-open-source-etude-smile-2013/\">Journal du Net parle des diff&eacute;rents CMS </a>du moment au travers de l&rsquo;analyse du <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.smile.fr/Livres-blancs/Gestion-de-contenu-et-GED/Les-CMS-open-source\">livre blanc de Smile</a>.</p>\n<h3>Flip Pong V</h3>\n<p>Une&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://tambourdeville.net/?page_id=256\">extension de flipbook</a> pour WordPress en HTML 5.</p>\n<h3>Des th&egrave;mes du mois de mai 2013</h3>\n<p>Une s&eacute;lection de <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wplift.com/free-wordpress-themes-may-2013\">th&egrave;mes r&eacute;cents dat&eacute;s de mai 2013 (en)</a>.</p>\n<h3>3 projets pour am&eacute;liorer WordPress</h3>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://rocketlift.com/news/three-projects-to-scale-up-wordpress/\">3 projets pour faire &eacute;voluer WordPress</a>&nbsp;(en).</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=jBXl3LIjGQE:1OpQF9IaVbI:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=jBXl3LIjGQE:1OpQF9IaVbI:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=jBXl3LIjGQE:1OpQF9IaVbI:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=jBXl3LIjGQE:1OpQF9IaVbI:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=jBXl3LIjGQE:1OpQF9IaVbI:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=jBXl3LIjGQE:1OpQF9IaVbI:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></a>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/jBXl3LIjGQE\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\">\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_